Poor Sinner! Take Example and Encouragement from Her! Preſume not of a ſmall Repentance

 for great Offences. Nor Deſpair of Pardon, be thy Offences never ſo great. From Her take better Heart and Care. She was Crown'd with Gods Forgiveneſs,
                        Pſ. 103. 4. but Commended that ſhe loved much.
